<h4 class="subheading">Business Analyst</h4>
<p><strong>Starting Salary: Circa £25,000 per annum (dependent on experience) + benefits</strong></p>
<p class="paragraph"><?php echo quin::$name;?> provides a range of financial products and services to corporate and personal customers. Our systems and IT infrastructure are developing to meet the growing and changing needs of the business.</p>
<p class="paragraph">We are therefore currently seeking to appoint a Business Analyst to further enhance and support the Group's IT development team.</p>
<p class="paragraph">Liaising with colleagues from across the Group, this person will be required to investigate and undertake analysis of business requirements. You will provide advice and expertise in relation to design and improvement of business systems and processes, and the use of appropriate analysis tools and methods. The role will also involve documenting agreed outcomes, preparing status reports and tracking progress against project plans and other assigned work as required.</p>
